<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font style=""><font style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;" size="2"><br></font></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial" style=""><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">It is important to understand how much money you can save by utilizing the Fleet One EDGE network. Fleets that utilize the EDGE network often save&nbsp;thousands of dollars more than those that don't. Below are a few highlights and tools to help you get the most out of the program.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><b><u><font size="2"><br></font></u></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><b><font size="2" style=""><u>The EDGE Fuel Network and Daily Price Feed</u></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><b><font size="2" style=""><br></font></b></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: small;">• Retail minus 10 cents&nbsp;at Pilot, Flying J and TA/Petro locations.</span></div><div style=""><font size="2"><br></font><font style="font-size: small;">• Take advantage of our larger discounts within our Cost Plus Network, which consists of&nbsp;</font><span style="font-size: small;"><b>AMBEST, Speedway, Kwik Trip, Kangaroo/Circle K, Sapp Bros., Petroleum Wholesale, Quick Fuel</b> and many others.</span></div><div style=""><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style=""><font size="2"><br></font><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2">Discounts will vary in our Cost Plus Network based on truck stop cost, but we see discounts on average of 20 cents per gallon throughout the year at many of these locations. You can refer to our daily price feed email for up-to-date prices. If you are not currently receiving daily pricing via email, <a href="http://benefits.fleetoneedge.com/pricefeedrequest">request the feed here</a>.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font size="2" style=""><u>Mobile App</u></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><u><font size="2"><br></font></u></b></div><div style=""><div style=""><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2">Have your drivers download the <b>Fleet One Mobile</b>&nbsp;app available on <a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/fleet-one-mobile/id919190970?mt=8">iOS</a> and <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wex.otrsitefinder">Android</a>. They can use registration code "735560" when registering to populate EDGE pricing.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><i><font size="2">(Instructions for registering: Click on three lines at top of the screen, then click registration. Enter fleet information and the registration code listed above. Wait up to 24 hours for EDGE pricing to populate in the mobile app).&nbsp;</font></i></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2">Stay tuned for the brand new Fleet One EDGE mobile app coming soon.</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font size="2"><br></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font size="2"><br></font></b></div><div style=""><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font size="2" style=""><u>Compliance Reporting</u></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><u><font size="2"><br></font></u></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2">We provide you with a monthly compliance email that shows you how well your fleet fueled within the Fleet One EDGE network, and how much your fleet saved within the given month. If you are not receiving this monthly email, please contact me.</font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style=""><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><font size="2" style=""><u>Educate Your Drivers</u></font></b></div><div style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b><u><font size="2"><br></font></u></b></div><div style=""><div style=""><font size="2">Please make sure your drivers understand the difference between In-network and Out-of-network purchases. If they are fueling Out-of-network, then you will not earn any discounts and will be subject to the $2.00 Out-of-network transaction fee.&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style=""><font size="2">I hope you find this information helpful in increasing your utilization of the EDGE network to get the most benefit. If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact me.&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">Thank you,</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><b>{!User.FirstName} {!User.LastName}</b>&nbsp;</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">Fleet One EDGE Benefits</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">866.840.7115</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">benefits@fleetoneedge.com</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><img src="https://wexinc--c.na64.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=0150g000004NtmV&amp;oid=00D700000009EOI" border="0" align="left" alt=""><br></div></font></div>]]></td>
